In a heavy bottom pan, melt 3 MUSKETEERS(R) Bars with milk, stirring constantly until smooth. Once melted, remove from heat immediately. Stir in the puffed cocoa cereal, mixing thoroughly. Drop by teaspoonfuls onto parchment-lined cookie sheets, making 40 mounds. Cool 5-10 minutes, or until cool enough to handle. With buttered fingers, roll mound into 1-inch balls. If desired, roll balls in chopped nuts and/or confectioners' sugar, or simply leave them plain.